----------------------------------------------------------------------
Adobe-Japan1 CID -> Unicode mapping data
----------------------------------------------------------------------

The generated file `cidunicode_japan1.go` (the `adobeJapan1CIDToUnicode`
table used to decode Identity-H/V Adobe-Japan1 CIDFonts that lack a
/ToUnicode CMap) is derived from the Adobe-Japan1-7 character collection's
`cid2code.txt`, distributed by Adobe in the adobe-type-tools/cmap-resources
repository. Only the CID, UniJIS-UCS2 and UniJIS-UTF32 columns are used; no
Adobe source code is incorporated.

  Source:  https://github.com/adobe-type-tools/cmap-resources
  File:    Adobe-Japan1-7/cid2code.txt
  Commit:  f5cf3bca7fdfeaceb77aa82847e974f2306c20b4 (2023-11-15)
